---
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
import SkillsGrid from "./SkillsGrid.astro";

const heading = "About";
---

<section id="about" class="px-4 text-xl">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <SectionHeader heading={heading} />
    <div class="space-y-6 ">
      <p>Based in Southern California, I enjoy creating clean, responsive web applications with modern web development tools like <span class="text-amber-600">React</span> and <span class="text-amber-600">Astro</span>.</p>
      <p>I’m particularly interested in web accessibility best practices, <span class="text-amber-600">inclusive design</span>, and crafting interfaces that are simple, fast, and intuitive to use.</p>
      <p>With a background in IT and working within <span class="text-amber-600">Agile</span> project management environments, I bring a collaborative mindset and strong communication skills to development teams.</p>
    </div>
    <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">My Skills</h3>
    <p>I'm a passionate learner and these are some of the technologies and tools I've used often.</p>
    <SkillsGrid />
  </div>
</section>
